<section id="problem">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="eyebrow reveal">The thesis</span>
    <h2 class="reveal" style="margin-top: 16px; max-width: 20ch;">
      Every agent demo treats inference as free. That's the error.
    </h2>
    <p class="reveal" style="margin-top: 20px; max-width: 64ch; font-size: 18px;">
      Compute is money. Stripe ships the wallet. NemoClaw isolates the process. NVIDIA
      sells the compute. None of them decide whether <em>this</em> job is worth burning
      Nemotron 3 Ultra on. Argus does — against a live ledger, per job, per turn.
    </p>
  </div>
